------------------------------
          Quark
------------------------------

Quark is a lightweight GPU rendered text editor.
*This is an early-stage project*

------------------
Build Instructions
------------------
Prerequisites:
- Clang/GCC

Linux / macOS:
1. Make sure glfw3 is compiled and setup
2. Build:
       ./build_<platform>.sh

Windows:
	Support is currently not there
	but trivial to add.

